****Build NGM:****

Required software:
cmake
zlib (Ubuntu: zlib1g-dev)
cudatoolkit
For BAM support Bamtools (http://sourceforge.net/projects/bamtools/) is required


1) Build MASon:

wget https://github.com/Cibiv/MASon/tarball/master -O MASon.tar.gz
tar xfvz MASon.tar.gz
cd Cibiv-MASon*
mkdir -p build/release
cd build/release/
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ../..
make
make install (root required)

If you don't have root permissions, please add the path to the MASon libs to yout LD_LIBRARY_PATH:

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=<mason path>

After building you find the compiled libraries in the "mason-trunk/bin" folder.


2) Build NGM:

wget https://github.com/Cibiv/NextGenMap/tarball/master -O NGM.tar.gz
tar xvfz NGM.tar.gz
cd Cibiv-NextGenMap*
mkdir -p build/release
cd build/release/
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ../..
make

cd ../../bin
./NGM

